{"tid":1776343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武做唔到，罷工做唔到，但罷消費應該做到掛","createTime":"2019-12-09T12:50:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T16:49:02.000Z","uid":58998,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"d5193bf6ef3c0be580d90c87c57b22f8204e3a1f","tid":1776343,"uid":58998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T12:50:30.000Z","msg":"嚟緊就聖誕節同除夕，依兩個節日對零售好重要，而且仲係由年輕人主導消費<br />\n所以話黃絲嘅消費力係依兩個節日仲大影響過新年<br />\n如果我地嗰個星期，可以做到罷消費，只用錢係必需品，最後就旺區都唔去<br />\n你話到時零售唔見幾多錢，政府搞到宵禁咁又幾肉酸，甚至係國際笑話<br />\n如果成功嘅，下年仲有大把節日可以玩，甚至平日都做得，你話零售行業有幾驚，佢地一定會俾壓力政府<br />\n最緊要係零損傷唔犯法，政府完全吹你唔脹<br />\n仲有兩個星期，我哋夠哂時間去文宣<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港俾政府搞成咁，仲過節洗錢咩</span></span>"},{"pid":"0a1628e6525d46a63497c0ff8b1b7383eb2cc342","tid":1776343,"uid":58998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T12:52:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"776795ade6b16c463af5fced7bb1087e0ca71279","tid":1776343,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T12:54:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">尋找黑警性暴力證人/受害者，協助國際遊說</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2640629789347426&amp;id=124616407615456\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2640629789347426%26id%3D124616407615456&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2F%2FsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=e3920b93\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2640629789347426&amp;id=124616407615456</a><br />\n<br />\nPost：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eDEkrT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eDEkrT</a><br />\n<br />\n//平等機會婦女聯席發言人區美寶稱，3個組織11月初共同發起控訴警察性暴力的國際聯署，截至本月7日收集到21國共85個團體聯署支持。為了向聯合國專家展開更有力游說，3個組織呼籲受害者主動聯絡他們並接受訪談，強調會保密。//<br />\n<br />\n我們現正收集抗爭者在抗爭期間／被捕後遭受警察性暴力對待的資料，作以下用途：<br />\n1. 協助受害人可以完整保留該事件之紀錄<br />\n2. 整理資料並製成 #ProtestToo 實錄，以作追究之用<br />\n3. 收集國際聯署（進行中），結合個案提交聯合國，爭取國際間關注及支持<br />\n4. 要求香港政府獨立、公正地徹查「反送中運動」發生的性暴力<br />\n<br />\n*個人資料及通訊紀錄在實錄完成後可按受訪者意願全部銷毀<br />\n詳情及相關安排請聯絡Tg @protesttoo"},{"pid":"c7aec1913cccb6da0a862a1686beaf0c1844d409","tid":1776343,"uid":343006,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:03:39.000Z","msg":"罷消費明明係零風險嘅抗議，希望大家都出分力，今年聖誕同新年唔好消費喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d0d952e99952ba7c9ed25a3fd0896ef4e372558","tid":1776343,"uid":58998,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c7aec1913cccb6da0a862a1686beaf0c1844d409","tid":1776343,"uid":343006,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:03:39.000Z","msg":"罷消費明明係零風險嘅抗議，希望大家都出分力，今年聖誕同新年唔好消費喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:07:31.000Z","msg":"無乜人理<br />\n大家覺得主動進攻先夠力量，但罷消費都好有力量<br />\n你仲可以零風險一直做落去"},{"pid":"8742a30282d814213d8d374c9bd01b3f41215832","tid":1776343,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:09:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bbRpVVk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbbRpVVk.png&h=3d9e7c29&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"adafb007ef830e946249d7eed220cc63b164394d","tid":1776343,"uid":95499,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:11:36.000Z","msg":"女朋友唔比 做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e0d10df55adce83f3de656550e5a5165d21f781","tid":1776343,"uid":58998,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"adafb007ef830e946249d7eed220cc63b164394d","tid":1776343,"uid":95499,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:11:36.000Z","msg":"女朋友唔比 做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:14:01.000Z","msg":"一齊係屋企煮飯仔，瘋狂扑嘢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.